  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/3ce557f6be86f95cdc7566bc8973c29d.poster.avif?t=1732311130\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/3ce557f6be86f95cdc7566bc8973c29d.webm?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/3ce557f6be86f95cdc7566bc8973c29d.mp4?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The objective of the game is to crawl through 20 levels. Along the way you earn gold, unlock skills and buy items. At each level you upgrade your Hero and unlock Skills to help you get further. As you go higher, the enemies get tougher. What worked before, may not work anymore. <br><br>There is no wrong way to play. You can brawl your way through the dungeon gulping Health and Stamina potions as you go or you can play more strategically and think your way through. It's up to you to figure out how to get through. <br><br>The mechanics of the game are quite simple. You create a Hero (fighter, archer or mage) and guide them through 20 different levels. You get to the next level by defeating all enemies and exiting the level. Replay the levels as much as you like.<br><br>Choose from 3 classes ( fighter, mage or archer ) and fully customize your hero:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Customize armor, weapons, accessories, hair, beards and even skin color<br></li><li> Over 60 different weapons and shields based on character and level<br></li><li> Accessorize your hero with bling, head gear, sun glasses and more<br></li><li> Different styles of game play based on character</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/69c4c823c45119d8a5d660b45555c749.poster.avif?t=1732311130\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/69c4c823c45119d8a5d660b45555c749.webm?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/69c4c823c45119d8a5d660b45555c749.mp4?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your character progress is saved at every level. Make changes to your character at anytime and replay the levels as often as you like. Leave the dungeon at anytime, make changes and get back in.<br><br>Unlock over 120 different skills based on character and level. Each class with its own unique skills to learn and master.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fireball / Fire Bolt / Fire Comet<br></li><li> Lightning Shot / Lightning Strike / Lightning Chain<br></li><li> Power Shot / Bleeding / Vine Spikes / Poison Shot<br></li><li> Ice Bolt / Ice Shot / Ice Spikes<br></li><li> Critical Hit / Ruinous Slash<br></li><li> Rage / Berserk<br></li><li> Melee attacks<br></li><li> and more</li></ul><br>Over 50 different enemies to slay:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Goblins<br></li><li> Ghouls<br></li><li> Trolls<br></li><li> Skeletons<br></li><li> Rogue Knights<br></li><li> Golems<br></li><li> Mechanoids<br></li><li> and more</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/6a6d0540a03b59ad5fc502a2e57dcf3d.poster.avif?t=1732311130\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/6a6d0540a03b59ad5fc502a2e57dcf3d.webm?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684390/extras/6a6d0540a03b59ad5fc502a2e57dcf3d.mp4?t=1732311130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
